&lt;li&gt;Assist with unloading and loading trucks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use warehouse management systems (WMS) to process incoming and outgoing goods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspect incoming products for quantity and part number accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
