&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean and organized work area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow safety procedures and company policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other duties as assigned by the supervisor or manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
