&lt;li&gt;3+ years of working knowledge of product development and/or product marketing experience with circuit breaker technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with networking technologies including cellular and ethernet highly desired&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidate must be well organized, self-motivated, and capable of seeing projects through to completion.&lt;/li&gt;
